NOUAKCHOTT, Mauritania, March 6, 2021/APO Group/ -- 
                                                        
                            In advance of the final of the 2021 CAF U-20 Cup of Nations, a joint press event entitled "Ceremony of African Unity" is being staged at the Palais des Congr√®s, Nouakchott, Mauritania on Saturday 6 March at 19:00* local time (20:00 Paris Time).
        
                                    
                    
                        
                                                
                        
                        
